 <p>     Refusing to install when stage1 doesn't work (to prevent bootloops)
 <p>v1.3 fixed lwvm patch (bug where 9.3.1 rootfs was ro)
 <p>v1.2 fixed a bug where having a passcode would disable untether
 <p>v1.1 fixed deepsleep bug
 <br>
 Currently supported device:
 <p>iPhone4,1: 9.3.4
